Author: PhoneWalletSanity
Text: All my bfs have been super skinny; the kind of guys who have zero appetite aside from coke and the occasional fast food meal and you can't get them to eat more. It's honestly super triggering but then I remind myself that I'm doing whatever I'm doing "for" me so whatever my SO does is up to them and I don't have to support them or anything unless they ask for help to be healthier.

Author: makeitfancee
Text: That must be hard. I myself have to be around my triggering mother and it sucks. Does your bf know you have an ed? Are you seeing a therapist of some sorts to talk about things like this?
